                        <interp inst="t18360404-name-1265" type="given" value="ALEXANDER"></interp>ALEXANDER ROBERTSON</persName>
                  </hi>. I had an appointment in the National pro<lb></lb>vincial Bank of England. I was in Fleet-street on the 4th of April, be<lb></lb>tween seven and eight o'clock—I did not feel any thing; but one of the witness asked me if I had lost any thing—I felt, and missed my hand<lb></lb>kerchief—it is lost altogether—it was a red and Yellow silk one—I did not observe the prisoner near me—he was taken about three yards from me.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
