                  </hi>. I am a patrol of St. Bride's I was in Fleet-street, talking to another witness—I saw the prisoner and another well-known</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="183604040231"></xptr>
               <p>pickpocket, named Martin, coming up—I saw the prisoner take the hand<lb></lb>kerchief from the prosecutor's pocket, and hand it to Martin—I received them both—Martin made his escape—he ran away with it in his hand, and left his hat behind him—he said, "It is no go this time, Thorp."</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner. Q.</hi> How do you know that the other got away with it? <hi rend="italic">Wit<lb></lb>ness</hi>. Because I saw you give it him.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
